Package com.tversity.airflinger.sdk.android.assets Description

Classes that provide a uniform access to media items, either local on the device, or remote on a media server.

Use LocalMediaProvider for accessing media items on the local device.
Accessing media items on a remote server is done with the Server.browseChildren() method.
